snippet.title: Amber Heard Has Officially Digged Her Own Grave | Celebrity news
snippet.description:
Amber Heard Has Officially Dug Her Own Grave. IS AMBER HEARD A GAME PLAYER?

Entertainment news about David Sherborne client's case with Amber Heard and Johnny Depp.
►►►Subscribe: https://bit.ly/3vX5q2R

Fans who are regularly updated on the situation between Johnny Depp as known as Jack sparrow and Aquaman actress Amber heard, her ex-wife attended the final hearing of the domestic abuse trial, where Amber got the lead. She thanked all her fans who supported her on social media. But this story isn’t ended yet, Johnny Depp considered this trial a total misjudged and called it an injustice. Depp’s Lawyers claimed a new trial according to them:

“The first trial’s judge “failed to properly assess her credibility by reference to documentary evidence, photographs, recordings or otherwise.”

What barrister David Sherborne, who is Depp’s lawyer, wants to bring to notice is Amber’s being untruthful in her pieces of evidence and statements. 
“….without taking account of or even acknowledging that Ms. Heard had been untruthful in her evidence, without testing her account against the documentary evidence and the evidence of other witnesses, and without making any findings that he disbelieved those witnesses,” 

Now from here the new story of a new trial starts, previous trial ended in amber’s favor but what this new trial is going to bring? Whether Depp has cut off the nose to spite the face or Amber this time dig her own grave?
So, Depp, this time accused her of showing fake charity documents to court as she promised to give a 7 million dollar settlement donation. This time Depp’s lawyers emerged after doing all of their homework.
▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬▬
